  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators' aim is to study the effect of pressure support ventilation versus neurally
      adjusted assist (NAVA) and controlled by patient in mechanically ventilated ALI/ARDS
      subjects.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      In this study, PSV is compared with NAVA and assisted mechanically ventilation controlled by
      patient through a button. Inclusion criteria are: assisted mechanically ventilated ALI/ARDS
      patients.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
